Text: Dashboard Report ENAIntegrated Solution Center has prepared a report called Monthly Dashboard for your business unit ENA for the month of February The purpose of this report is to provide you with information submitted through the SAP Hotline This report was carefully selected to summarize t he criticality of issues pertaining to an area as explained further in the report The items listed are broken down by the number of tickets and t he number of exceptions per priority level of critical urgent high medium and low The report also addresses the grand total of tickets and total number of exceptions these exceptions are based against the SLAs The ISC recognizes the importance of communication associated with our customers and is ready to provide you this information on a monthly basis Therefore please expect this report to be generated and provided to you via email on a monthly basis Should you encounter any questions please contact Martha Utley Ext
